org.epics.pvmanager

Class CacheCollector<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.epics.pvmanager.CacheCollector<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type contained in the cache
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Collector<T,List<T>>, ReadFunction<List<T>>, WriteFunction<T>

    public class CacheCollector<T>
extends Object
implements Collector<T,List<T>>
    Collects value at read rate and keeps the last n.

    The values are returned oldest value first. When maxSize is reached, the oldest values are discarded.

    Author:
    carcassi
